  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Loss of sense of smell and taste has been anecdotally reported during the covid-19 epidemic.
      The study investigators wanted to describe the prevalence of olfactory and gustatory
      dysfunction and assess the factors associated with positive SARS-CoV-2 infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
